</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3306008001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove oil seals from right case (1) using special tool, if necessary.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C019">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-15410">
09925–15410
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A330026.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.889mm" ver = "01" gw = "130" gh = "114"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove oil seals from left case, if necessary.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3306008002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
When installing oil seal No.2 (1) and No.3 (2) to right case (3) using special tool as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Apply grease to oil seal lip.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C020">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-15410">
09925–15410
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI Super Grease A" id = "M3C007" uid = "1126491901">
<m-part>
“A”
</m-part>
<m-desc>
